# {{logic}} A [[logical]] [[system]] involving theory of classes, developed by [[w:Stanislaw_Lesniewski|Stanislaw Lesniewski]] (1886-1939).
# {{computer science}} A [[structure]] of [[concept]]s or [[entity|entities]] within a [[domain]], organized by [[relationship]]s; a system [[model]].

